divs: sighting detailswent outside to lock up sheds and looked up at stars because it is clear. saw object moving directly above me moving steadily north. straight line, consistent speed, no sound, had a star like appearance, steady white light in color, about 20,0000 feet up, was flying due north. have seen objects like this many times and they are always not in the flight paths and always between 9 and 11 pm. i don't stay up late up at 5:30 am every day. the date is 09\09\13
